{"tid":1575910,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"講句嘢就畀人打！","createTime":"2019-09-17T04:20:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T04:40:33.000Z","uid":231373,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4290091c8063521d5d829cf4a9f77241bafb1f88","tid":1575910,"uid":231373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:20:37.000Z","msg":"記得share俾廢老睇 成間酒樓清靜晒 無晒廢老話自己好好打<br />\n<br />\n昨晚(16日)接近11時，一名姓嚴62歲男子於新蒲崗寧遠街附近一條「連儂隧道」，疑政見問題與大約10名青年男女爭執，部分人身穿黑色衫褲；繼而互有肢體碰撞，嚴遭人拳打腳踢倒地，復被人淋膠水，他頭及手腳受傷，兇徒得逞後逃去。<br />\n救護員到場將事主送院治理，他抵院時向在場記者表示，「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">講句嘢就畀人打！</span></span>」，案件列襲擊致造成實際身體傷害，警方正展開深入調查，並追查兇徒下落。<br />\n據了解，事發時有人走進隧道襲擊在場人士，未幾即有兩批人拉扯碰撞，嚴被推跌在地，並有人向其淋膠水，場面混亂，在場數名女子見狀勸止，涉事者四散，現場地上遺下血漬、膠水及散落一地的紙張。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190917/mobile/bkn-20190917002126358-0917_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190917%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190917002126358-0917_00822_001.html&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rZq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=aec81ef5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190917/mobile/bkn-20190917002126358-0917_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"856341503d8661acd88af064e83dc94369ece5c5","tid":1575910,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:21:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eac2842b19aaebfe2c0a74cfab9f342a5079c319","tid":1575910,"uid":75994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:23:08.000Z","msg":"講緊比休班黑警打嗎?"},{"pid":"1bc3880a01b26eedcecd3affe325edb103cd3c05","tid":1575910,"uid":231373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor